# Flutter Complete Dark Mode System (Riverpod)

I want to implement a complete, scalable, production-ready Dark Mode system across my Flutter application using **Riverpod (flutter_riverpod)**. The implementation should follow Flutter best practices, Material 3, and Clean Architecture.

## Objective

Refactor the entire application so every UI component automatically adapts to Light and Dark themes without using hardcoded colors.

The implementation should be maintainable, reusable, and easy to extend.

---

# Theme Management

Use Riverpod for state management.

Create:

* ThemeProvider
* ThemeNotifier (StateNotifier or Notifier)
* ThemeState
* ThemeService
* AppTheme

The provider should expose:

* current ThemeMode
* isDarkMode
* isLightMode
* isSystemMode
* toggleTheme()
* setLightTheme()
* setDarkTheme()
* setSystemTheme()

The selected theme must update the entire application instantly.

---

# Theme Persistence

Persist the selected theme using SharedPreferences.

Requirements:

* Save selected ThemeMode.
* Restore it on app startup.
* Default to System Theme if no preference exists.
* Never lose the selected theme after restarting the app.

---

# Theme Structure

Create:

lib/
├── core/
│    ├── theme/
│    │      app_theme.dart
│    │      light_theme.dart
│    │      dark_theme.dart
│    │      app_colors.dart
│    │      app_gradients.dart
│    │      app_text_theme.dart
│    │      app_extensions.dart
│    │      theme_provider.dart
│    │      theme_service.dart

Everything related to theming should live inside this folder.

---

# Material 3

Use Material 3.

Use ColorScheme instead of manually assigning colors.

Example:

* primary
* secondary
* tertiary
* surface
* surfaceContainer
* background
* error
* outline
* shadow
* inversePrimary

Avoid deprecated properties.

---

# Color System

Remove every hardcoded color from the project.

Replace colors for:

* Scaffold
* AppBar
* Drawer
* NavigationBar
* BottomNavigationBar
* BottomSheet
* Dialog
* PopupMenu
* SnackBar
* Card
* Container
* Divider
* Border
* Shadow
* Chip
* Badge
* Checkbox
* Switch
* Radio
* Slider
* Progress Indicator
* CircularProgressIndicator
* LinearProgressIndicator
* Icons
* Text
* Buttons
* FloatingActionButton
* SearchBar
* SearchView
* Dropdown
* MenuAnchor
* TextField
* OTP Fields
* ListTile
* ExpansionTile
* TabBar
* TabView
* NavigationRail
* DataTable
* Grid
* Charts
